## Accessibility

- Always include ARIA labels: `aria-label="Execute command"`
- Keyboard navigation: `tabIndex={0}` with `onKeyDown` handlers
- Screen reader support: `<span className="sr-only">Loading...</span>`

## Icon Usage

Prefer text indicators over icons:
```tsx
// Prefer
<span className="font-mono text-green-400">[OK]</span>
<span className="font-mono text-red-400">[ERROR]</span>
<span className="font-mono text-yellow-400">[WARN]</span>
```

## Animation Rules

Keep minimal:
- Terminal typing: `initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 10 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}`
- Blinking cursor: `<span className="animate-pulse">_</span>`
- Loading (only element with border-radius): `rounded-full border-4 border-primary border-t-transparent animate-spin`

## DO NOT

- ❌ Use border-radius (except loaders)
- ❌ Use gradients or shadows  
- ❌ Use custom colors outside globals.css
- ❌ Use decorative elements
- ❌ Mix font families (only system and mono)
- ❌ Use opacity for disabled states